-- 3. Heliocare 360 Gel Oil Free Touch SPF50+
update public.products set description = $desc$
<h3>Is Heliocare 360 Gel Oil Free Touch right for you?</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Oily or combination skin</strong> — The oil-free gel formula controls sebum production so your skin stays matte from morning to evening without midday touch-ups.</li>
<li><strong>Acne-prone patients</strong> — Non-comedogenic formula will not block pores or trigger breakouts — safe to use daily even during active acne treatment.</li>
<li><strong>Patients after Dermapen or acne treatments</strong> — Provides the essential post-procedure UV protection your newly treated skin needs without adding any oiliness.</li>
<li><strong>Men who want a simple, invisible SPF</strong> — The gel consistency absorbs like water and leaves no detectable residue — the easiest SPF routine possible.</li>
<li><strong>Humid climate wearers</strong> — Specifically formulated for high-heat environments where most sunscreens break down and become greasy within hours.</li>
</ul>

<h3>How Heliocare 360 Gel Oil Free Touch works — the science</h3>
<p>The <strong>mattifying gel base</strong> uses a sebum-absorbing polymer network that actively soaks up excess oil throughout the day, maintaining a consistently matte finish without ever feeling dry or tight. <strong>Fernblock®</strong> provides cellular-level UV defence that supplements the 360° broad-spectrum filter system protecting against UVA, UVB, infrared and blue light. The <strong>non-comedogenic formulation</strong> is specifically engineered with oily skin in mind — every ingredient is selected to deliver maximum protection without any ingredient that could trigger sebum overproduction or pore congestion.</p>

<h3>What you will notice — and when</h3>
<p><strong>Immediately:</strong> Applies like water, absorbs in seconds. Skin feels clean and matte — not tight, not shiny.<br><strong>Week 1–2:</strong> Midday shine is noticeably reduced. Makeup lasts longer. Skin stops feeling like it needs blotting by noon.<br><strong>Month 1+:</strong> With consistent UV protection, sun-triggered sebum surges reduce. Pores appear smaller and skin tone is more even.</p>

<h3>How to use Heliocare 360 Gel Oil Free Touch</h3>
<ol>
<li>Apply as the final step of your morning routine after any targeted treatments — this is the last product before you leave the house.</li>
<li>Apply a generous, even layer across the entire face, including the T-zone. Do not skimp — under-application reduces SPF level.</li>
<li>Allow 20–30 seconds to absorb. Makeup can be applied immediately after.</li>
<li>Reapply every 2 hours in direct sunlight. The Heliocare Compacts SPF50 compact is ideal for midday reapplication over makeup.</li>
</ol>

<h3>Key ingredients &amp; what they do</h3>
