<tr><td>Thiamidol</td><td>Next-generation tyrosinase inhibitor — blocks the enzyme responsible for melanin production at the source, reducing new pigment formation with each application.</td></tr>
<tr><td>Niacinamide (Vitamin B3)</td><td>Inhibits the transfer of melanin from melanocytes to skin cells — effectively keeping produced melanin from reaching the surface and forming visible dark spots.</td></tr>
