<li><strong>Beach and holiday families</strong> — Full-body application for a family of four requires a large format SPF. The 200ml paediatric lotion covers everyone without the anxiety of running out.</li>
<li><strong>Parents of children with eczema or sensitive skin</strong> — The 100% mineral, fragrance-free formula is safe for the most reactive skin from 6 months of age.</li>
