<p>The spray delivery system atomises the <strong>Fernblock®-enriched SPF50 formula</strong> into fine, even droplets that deposit a uniform protective film across large skin surface areas in seconds. The <strong>broad-spectrum UVA and UVB filter complex</strong> is suspended in an alcohol-assisted vehicle that evaporates quickly on contact, leaving the active filters bonded to the skin surface without tackiness or residue. <strong>Fernblock®</strong> provides the same cellular-level photoprotection as the full Heliocare range, adding biological UV defence alongside the topical filter layer. The 200ml size is specifically calibrated for body applications — which require significantly more product than facial use to achieve the stated SPF level.</p>

